{"tid":1590333,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter國際文宣戰線]手足召集","createTime":"2019-09-23T16:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T23:55:33.000Z","uid":151525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f7e320cba112f38daf73a6b365a7b65094ac6f","tid":1590333,"uid":151525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n有黑警暴行嘅圖或片<br />\n請多tag國際組織 外國政要 新聞媒體<br />\nTag完先好出tweet<br />\n<br />\n由Day 1推極都推唔到hashtags上熱門<br />\n到近期開始見到有部分hashtags長期trending/&gt;1K tweets in the past hour<br />\n伴隨香港人權民主法案等呼聲增加<br />\nTwitter國際文宣戰線係有用㗎!!!<br />\n<br />\n近期見開始少咗手足出tweet/RT <br />\n利申我自己都懶咗一排<br />\n但10.1仲有一個禮拜 香港人權民主法案正準備開始審議<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位Twitter國際文宣手足 歸位啦!</span></strong></span><br />\nKeep住道火!!!!! Keep住個noise!!!!! 要全世界一齊賀佢老母國慶!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n以下各tag供參；如果有建議，請出招，開放討論。<br />\n@washingtonpost<br />\n@BBCWorld<br />\n@CBSNews<br />\n@cnni<br />\n@FoxNews<br />\n@time<br />\n@nytimes<br />\n@reuters<br />\n@FT <br />\n@latimes<br />\n@abc<br />\n@guardiannews<br />\n@CNETNews<br />\n@UNHumanRights <br />\n@hrw <br />\n@amnesty <br />\n@EUCouncil <br />\n@EUCouncilPress <br />\n@SpeakerPelosi <br />\n@realDonaldTrump <br />\n@marcorubio <br />\n@solomonyue<br />\n@senatemajldr <br />\n@CanadianPM <br />\n@10DowningStreet <br />\n@UKParliament"},{"pid":"58d80f483b46d4e0ba0ab462afd09f2391a198ba","tid":1590333,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"d8418f7751d668519aa27181f2cbc8dcbd277d87","tid":1590333,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:15.000Z